headline: Better Artificial Intelligence Stock: Super Micro Computer vs. Dell Technologies
summary: Despite the extreme stock market volatility at the start of 2025, the artificial intelligence (AI) revolution is moving full steam ahead.  At the core of this transformation are high-performance data centers, which play a critical role in the AI ecosystem.  Two leading companies in this space are Super Micro Computer (NASDAQ: SMCI) and Dell Technologies (NYSE: DELL), which supply the essential server equipment and storage hardware to run AI workloads.
